---
<section id="model-output" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Model Output</h2>
    
    <div class="grid-2-col">
      <div class="explanation">
        <p>The classifier returns the highest-scoring label from the model output.</p>
        <p>Labels follow a crop and condition format such as <code>Crop___Disease</code> or <code>Crop___healthy</code>.</p>
        <p>The app converts raw labels into readable crop and disease names.</p>
        
        <div class="note">
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> The current label file contains 68 crop and condition labels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="example-panel">
        <h3>Example Diagnosis</h3>
        
        <div class="conversion-block">
          <div class="label-box">
            <span class="label-type">Raw label</span>
            <code class="raw-label">Tomato___Late_blight</code>
          </div>
          <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>
          <div class="label-box success">
            <span class="label-type">Displayed result</span>
            <span class="display-label">Tomato - Late blight</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="output-list-container">
          <h4>Output Fields</h4>
          <ul class="output-list">
            <li>Crop name</li>
            <li>Disease or healthy status</li>
            <li>Confidence percentage</li>
            <li>Symptoms</li>
            <li>Possible causes</li>
            <li>Management guidance</li>
            <li>Processed leaf preview</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .explanation {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  .explanation p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  code {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-subtle-border);
  }

  .note {
    margin-top: var(--space-l);
    padding: var(--space-m);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-brand);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .example-panel {
    background-color: var(--color-raised-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-subtle-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .example-panel h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
  }

  .conversion-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-s);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    padding: var(--space-m);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .label-box {
    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--space-m);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-subtle-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background-color: var(--color-raised-surface);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .label-box.success {
    border-color: var(--color-success);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .label-type {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-muted-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .raw-label {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .display-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-success);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }

  .arrow {
    color: var(--color-muted-text);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }

  .output-list-container h4 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
  }

  .output-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-s);
  }

  .output-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-l);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .output-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px;
    color: var(--color-brand);
  }
</style>
